email_verified_at\":\"2021-06-01T18:37:14.000000Z\",\"created_at\":\"2021-06-01T18:37:15.000000Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2021-06-01T18:37:15.000000Z\",\"active\":0}}}', NULL, '2021-06-17 08:44:06', '2021-06-17 08:44:06'),
